      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I am so excited to show you this beauty. Honestly, it\u2019s in absolute pristine condition\u2014it looks and drives just like it did the day it rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, keeping it tucked away in the garage and making sure it\u2019s always spotless. If you\u2019re looking for that perfect, like-new experience without the brand-new price tag, this is the one for you. Come take a look, you\u2019re going to love it!",
