    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) finished in Carbon Black. This example features the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six, utilizing individual throttle bodies and high-pressure double-VANOS to produce 333 hp with an 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and the factory variable M differential lock. This chassis has undergone proactive subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul. Suspension kinematics remain sharp with refreshed bushings and factory-spec dampening. The exterior retains its original deep luster with zero oxidation, while the interior displays no bolster wear or pixel degradation. A mechanically flawless specimen for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 47500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
