    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional specimen that redefines the standard for 'mint' condition. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, retaining its showroom luster with a deep, swirl-free ceramic-coated finish. Inside, the cabin remains untouched by time; the premium leather still carries that distinctive factory aroma, with absolutely zero wear on the seat bolsters, steering wheel, or touchpoints. Every service has been performed ahead of schedule at authorized dealerships, documented in a comprehensive maintenance binder that accompanies the car. From the flawless alloy wheels wrapped in fresh high-performance tires to the pristine undercarriage, this is a collector-grade vehicle for the most discerning enthusiast. No accidents, no smoke, and no imperfections\u2014just pure, unadulterated automotive excellence that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line.",
